               <head>Tuhfah-i tazah</head>
               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of Tuḥfah-'i tāzah by Khayr al-Dīn Muḥammad Ilāhābādī</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/no2002019032 http://lccn.loc.gov/n82017475 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85064914" n="1" xml:id="Uk_IO_Islamic_3911-item1">
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" type="supplied" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164656303.0x000001 viaf_10686487">Khayr al-Dīn Muḥammad Ilāhābādī</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="per" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164656303.0x000001 viaf_10686487" type="supplied">خير الدّين محمّد الٰه آبادى</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="work_583">Tuḥfah-'i tāzah</title>
                     <title xml:lang="per" key="work_583">تحفهٴ تازه</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>Alternative title: <term xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc">Balvandnāmah</term>
                        </p>
                        <p>Alternative title: <term xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc">Tārīkh-i Balvandī</term>
                        </p>
                        <p>History of the landowners or <term xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc">zamīndār</term>s of <name type="place">Benares</name> / <name type="place">Varanasi</name> (<name type="place">Uttar Pradesh</name>, <name type="place">India</name>), from the period of <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="person_f7696" role="subject">Mansārām</persName> to the deposition  of <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164658461.0x000001 viaf_46425344" role="subject">Chayt Singh</persName> (<persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164658461.0x000001 viaf_46425344" role="subject">Chait Singh</persName>), in <date calendar="Hijri-qamari">1195</date> / <date calendar="Gregorian">1781</date>
                        </p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="per" xml:lang="per">Persian</textLang>
                     <note/>
                     <filiation>Copied from a manuscript obtained at <name type="place">Jaunpur</name> (see <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="viaf_8170991" role="oth">William Irvine</persName>'s note on a flyleaf of I.O.Islamic 3894) through the mediation of <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="person_f7724" role="oth">Munshīʾ Ṣadr al-Dīn Aḥmad</persName>, <term xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc">taḥṣīldār</term> and <term xml:lang="en">magistrate</term> of <name type="place">Farrukhabad District</name>
                     </filiation>
